OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMost areas will see some sunny
OL,6,Fintervals, although plenty of showers
OL,7,Fare also likely. The showers could be
OL,8,Fheavy and possibly thundery, merging
OL,9,Fin places to give some longer spells
OL,10,Fof rain. Feeling cool, with a blustery
OL,11,Fwind for many.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FShowers gradually becoming
OL,14,Fmore focused across northern and
OL,15,Fwestern areas during the overnight
OL,16,Fperiod. Otherwise there will be clear
OL,17,Fspells. Breezy, especially in the
OL,18,Fnorth, and chilly in rural spots.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
