OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FFriday will be a drier day
OL,6,Fwith sunny spells and lighter winds.
OL,7,FStill some mostly light showers,
OL,8,Fespecially in the north and west. Rain
OL,9,Farriving in the southwest later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
